          "date": "2013-03-06 11:32:11.000000000",
          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-398 nrs: Increase module usage count for external policies",
        "message": "LU-398 nrs: Increase module usage count for external policies\n\nIncrease the module usage count for policies that have registered\nfrom other modules; the count is increased once when the first\ninstance of the policy is started, and decreased when the last\ninstance of the policy is stopped. This prevents the external\nmodule from being unloaded when an instance of one of the\npolicies it contains may be handling an RPC.\n\nSigned-off-by: Nikitas Angelinas <nikitas_angelinas@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I5b3640ad169d70f3a04e5685e6afa71ea8c8e448\nOracle-bug-id: b=13634\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-73\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
